OL,3,CFlexible working laws could reduce
OL,4,Cregional inequality, Business
OL,5,CSecretary says
OL,7,FFlexible working laws could reduce
OL,8,Fregional inequality and contribute to
OL,9,Fproductivity, Business Secretary
OL,10,FJonathan Reynolds said, as he
OL,11,Fcriticised the Conservative Party for
OL,12,F"declaring war on people working from
OL,13,Fhome".
OL,15,FMr Reynolds also voiced his support
OL,16,Ffor increasing the minimum wage to
OL,17,Fensure those in work are guaranteed "a
OL,18,Fdecent quality of life".
