OL,3,CFlexible working laws could reduce
OL,4,Cregional inequality, Business
OL,5,CSecretary says
OL,7,FHe said: "We've had flexible working
OL,8,Flaws for quite some time in the UK.
OL,10,F"I think where people reach agreement
OL,11,Fwith their employer ... it does
OL,12,Fcontribute to productivity, it does
OL,13,Fcontribute to their resilience, their
OL,14,Fability to stay working for an
OL,15,Femployer."
OL,17,F"The UK has very significant regional
OL,18,Finequality. It could play a
OL,19,Fsignificant contribution to tackling
OL,20,Fthat," he added.
