OL,5,CSecretary says
OL,7,FHe did concede that there are
OL,8,Fsituations when it is "legitimate to
OL,9,Fneed the workforce in the office",
OL,10,Fsuch as when new employees need to
OL,11,Flearn from those more experienced.
OL,13,FOn the Tories approach to workers'
OL,14,Frights, he said: "Jacob Rees-Mogg made
OL,15,Fthis big thing as (then) business
OL,16,Fsecretary (in) declaring war on people
OL,17,Fworking from home.
